<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sample Report</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

  .container {
      background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    th,
    td {
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

  .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1><%= data.title %></h1>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Report Overview</h2>
    <p><%= data.content %></p>
    <p>This is a sample report for demonstration purposes, showcasing basic text and image layout to meet your initial understanding of report styles.</p>
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,<%= data.logo %>" alt="Sample Image">
    <h2>Details</h2>
    <h3>Market Research Data</h3>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Product Category</th>
        <th>Sales (10k RMB)</th>
        <th>Market Share (%)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Electronics</td>
        <td>500</td>
        <td>30</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Home Goods</td>
        <td>300</td>
        <td>20</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Food & Beverage</td>
        <td>400</td>
        <td>25</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <h3>Key Findings</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Electronics sales lead, but market competition is intense.</li>
      <li>Home goods demand shows steady growth.</li>
      <li>Food & beverage industry needs to focus on innovation to increase market share.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <p>Dynamic Content</p>
  <% if (data.items && data.items.length > 0) { %>
    <h3>Project List</h3>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <% data.items.forEach(item => { %>
        <li><%= item %></li>
      <% }) %>
    </ul>
  <% } %>
  <div class="footer">
    &copy; 2025 All Rights Reserved
  </div>
</body>

</html>
